@startuml UC1: Place Order - Duplicate Order Error

!theme plain

autonumber

actor User
participant "System" as System
participant "Server" as Server

== Menu Selection ==

User -> System: Press "Select Menu"
System -> User: Display OrderUI

== Order Attempt ==

User -> System: Press "Select Dinner"
System -> System: Save Dinner
System -> User: Display ServeStyle

User -> System: Press "Select ServeStyle"
System -> User: Display Additional Options

User -> System: Adjust Quantity
User -> System: Press "Select"
System -> Server: Check Duplicate Order

Server -> Server: Detect Duplicate Order\n(Same Request ID or\nRequest within 50 seconds)

Server -> System: Duplicate Order Error
System -> User: Display Error Message\n("Same order was recently created")

@enduml
